isFindMembersFilter

public static boolean isFindMembersFilter(DiscoveryFilter filter)
Determine if a filter is for following existing member links (from a group to member elements).It is expected that:
  • useExistingMember == true
  • unit is not null
  • requirements is non-empty
  • the interpreters on the requirements is OutCardinality

Parameters:
filter - the filter
Returns:
true if the filter is for finding the hostees of a unit.

inMemberReq - the member requirement defining the "in" membership requirement may be null (indicating that it can be a member of any group)
